VirMach now offers shared hosting through our sister brand "VPShared." While we still offer webhosting on our main brand, these services are low-price annual services, packed with lots of features. Our webhosting runs on the same powerful hardware as our VPS nodes: Dual E5 Xeon Processors and Solid State Drives in RAID 10.

All packages include cPanel, running on CloudLinux. Our cheapest package includes a shared IP address, while all others have dedicated IP addresses included at no additional cost. Features include 10Gbps of DDoS protection, free SSL through Let's Encrypt, as well as free daily backups. One-click installs are available through Softaculous for quick setup, and the same great support is available as our main brand.


